---
title: Chilled Tofu and Shrimp Noodle Salad with Creamy Peanut Dressing
description: This chilled noodle dish is perfect for a sunny day! The peanut dressing is fully-loaded with punchy flavours and a touch of heat. Textures from crisp sweet peppers combined with golden sauteed tofu bites, tender shrimp and soft noodles make this an easy winner!
